1
00:00:29,620 --> 00:00:32,980
=The Secret of the Lost Pearl=

2
00:00:33,020 --> 00:00:34,940
=Episode 5=
(Fiction. Do not imitate.)

3
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:35,840
Chubby.

4
00:00:36,200 --> 00:00:37,040
Get over here.

5
00:00:37,100 --> 00:00:37,950
Got it.

6
00:00:38,070 --> 00:00:39,070
Let's move together.

7
00:00:42,420 --> 00:00:43,270
Go.

8
00:00:43,390 --> 00:00:44,240
No more sweetness?

9
00:00:46,110 --> 00:00:46,950
One.

10
00:00:47,430 --> 00:00:48,270
Two.

11
00:00:49,150 --> 00:00:49,990
Three.

12
00:00:51,430 --> 00:00:52,270
One.

13
00:00:53,110 --> 00:00:53,950
Two.

14
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:55,440
Three.

15
00:00:57,430 --> 00:00:58,270
One.

16
00:00:59,240 --> 00:01:00,080
Two.

17
00:01:00,940 --> 00:01:01,800
Three.

18
00:01:01,920 --> 00:01:02,760
Go.

19
00:01:03,880 --> 00:01:04,840
Already on it.

20
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:05,710
One.

21
00:01:06,790 --> 00:01:07,630
Two.

22
00:01:07,983 --> 00:01:09,220
- Where's the trigger?
- Three.

23
00:01:09,950 --> 00:01:10,790
Where's the trigger?

24
00:01:10,790 --> 00:01:12,950
The trigger?

25
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:14,120
Where is it?

26
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:16,150
Don't scare him.

27
00:01:16,350 --> 00:01:17,200
He's got asthma.

28
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:18,280
You might make him collapse.

29
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:21,920
Find that trigger.

30
00:01:23,230 --> 00:01:25,590
It's right behind this stand.

31
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:27,000
We already checked there.

32
00:01:27,070 --> 00:01:27,976
There's nothing at all.

33
00:01:28,070 --> 00:01:28,910
Are you kidding me?

34
00:01:29,150 --> 00:01:31,310
It's right behind it.

35
00:01:31,870 --> 00:01:35,120
Once Chen opens the lock,

36
00:01:35,150 --> 00:01:36,230
this mechanism will shift,

37
00:01:36,230 --> 00:01:37,870
and the trigger will show itself.

38
00:01:38,310 --> 00:01:40,310
Lu, it's almost ready outside.

39
00:01:40,590 --> 00:01:41,730
How's it going on your side?

40
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:42,950
Well.

41
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:44,790
I'm about done too.

42
00:01:46,150 --> 00:01:47,350
I...

43
00:01:47,350 --> 00:01:49,430
- Lu, are you ready?
- My asthma's acting up.

44
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:52,070
Lu! Lu!

45
00:01:52,070 --> 00:01:53,040
You okay?

46
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:54,000
No, I'm not.

47
00:01:54,070 --> 00:01:54,910
Come here.

48
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:56,950
Come on.

49
00:01:57,430 --> 00:01:58,590
Are you even human?

50
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:01,000
His asthma's really bad.

51
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,070
It could kill him.

52
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,840
Go get his medicine!

53
00:02:05,750 --> 00:02:06,620
Where's your inhaler?

54
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:07,950
I forgot.

55
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,200
Which pocket?

56
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,360
Which side?

57
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:15,960
Hand it over.

58
00:02:19,310 --> 00:02:20,520
Not bad, Lu.

59
00:02:20,531 --> 00:02:21,520
Several days apart.

60
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,840
It feels like it's been forever?

61
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:27,800
You guys planned this ahead, huh?

62
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,590
Of course.

63
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:30,960
Chen Youxi,

64
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,470
it's too risky to go in like that.

65
00:02:33,910 --> 00:02:34,750
I have an idea.

66
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,240
It's all on you now.

67
00:02:40,150 --> 00:02:44,080
Drop your weapons!

68
00:02:44,190 --> 00:02:45,430
What are you shouting for?

69
00:02:46,079 --> 00:02:47,092
Are you out of your mind?

70
00:02:47,150 --> 00:02:47,990
You...

71
00:02:49,030 --> 00:02:49,910
Bring her out.

72
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:51,080
Move.

73
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:52,640
Come out.

74
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,400
Get over here.

75
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,360
Stop right there.

76
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:58,560
- Let her go!
- Hurry up!

77
00:02:58,630 --> 00:03:00,120
Your boss is in our hands.

78
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,750
Can't you see what's happening?

79
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:04,520
Weren't you acting tough just now?

80
00:03:04,750 --> 00:03:06,240
Try facing me.

81
00:03:06,910 --> 00:03:08,310
- Don't move.
- Chen.

82
00:03:08,430 --> 00:03:09,630
It's done.

83
00:03:09,750 --> 00:03:11,560
Lu, you deserve half the credit.

84
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:13,080
Come on, everyone.

85
00:03:13,590 --> 00:03:14,800
Stand on this side.

86
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,360
Let me see you; move it.

87
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,280
Get over there.

88
00:03:17,630 --> 00:03:19,120
- Hurry.
- Move it.

89
00:03:20,990 --> 00:03:21,840
Come on.

90
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,750
Alright, turn around.

91
00:03:23,870 --> 00:03:25,470
Turn! Don't just freeze there.

92
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,150
Put the gun down.

93
00:03:29,310 --> 00:03:31,360
Stay down! Pairs of two.

94
00:03:31,870 --> 00:03:33,000
Tie your shoelaces together.

95
00:03:34,590 --> 00:03:35,430
Tie the shoelaces.

96
00:03:35,470 --> 00:03:36,910
Why are you staring at me?

97
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:37,840
Hurry, tie them.

98
00:03:38,150 --> 00:03:38,990
Tie them up.

99
00:03:40,910 --> 00:03:41,750
Lu.

100
00:03:43,310 --> 00:03:44,150
Go now.

101
00:03:44,430 --> 00:03:45,270
Chase!

102
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:51,560
Chen, good for you.

103
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,840
The Four Bureau Star Lock?

104
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:54,190
You almost fooled us too.

105
00:03:54,316 --> 00:03:55,496
The ancestor wrote about this.

106
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,075
But it's not meant to be used this way.

107
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,120
Move!

108
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:05,933
Once we cross this cliff,

109
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,139
the car's behind that rock.

110
00:04:07,150 --> 00:04:07,990
Let her go later.

111
00:04:08,750 --> 00:04:09,840
Come on, she looks nice.

112
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:11,030
Let me get to know her a bit.

113
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,400
Fine, then you stay here with her.

114
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,240
Buy us some time.

115
00:04:13,250 --> 00:04:14,090
No, no.

116
00:04:14,090 --> 00:04:15,483
I'll choose friendship over love.

117
00:04:15,494 --> 00:04:16,640
Who said anything about love?

118
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,640
Love takes time to grow.

119
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:18,910
Don't move.

120
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,270
Drop your guns.

121
00:04:20,510 --> 00:04:21,750
Once we get out safely,

122
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,190
I'll let her go for sure.

123
00:04:23,310 --> 00:04:24,600
We don't buy that.

124
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:26,600
Anyway, she's in my hands.

125
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:28,830
Or you can choose to risk her life.

126
00:04:29,830 --> 00:04:30,920
Drop the gun.

127
00:04:33,270 --> 00:04:34,310
Put the gun down.

128
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:44,680
I'm letting you go now.

129
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,270
Let's part ways here

130
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:47,870
and forget each other for good.

131
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,440
Chubby.

132
00:04:57,630 --> 00:04:58,680
Hold on!

133
00:04:59,390 --> 00:05:00,800
- Don't move!
- Bai Lingling.

134
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:02,260
Bai Lingling, don't do anything rash.

135
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:03,830
Help me, Chen!

136
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,160
Chen Youxi,

137
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:09,040
before I cut this thin parachute cord,

138
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,830
find the tomb's location for me.

139
00:05:11,950 --> 00:05:12,790
I promise you.

140
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:13,833
I promise I'll find it.

141
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:14,920
Get him up first.

142
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:15,770
Pull him up.

143
00:05:15,780 --> 00:05:17,070
Hurry up, pull me!

144
00:05:17,310 --> 00:05:18,390
This is way too dangerous.

145
00:05:18,950 --> 00:05:19,890
Are you messing with me?

146
00:05:20,070 --> 00:05:21,920
The trick just now isn't enough?

147
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:22,960
I'm not a fool.

148
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:24,826
Stop wasting words with him.

149
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,030
Throw him down first.

150
00:05:26,041 --> 00:05:27,222
- Huang Long.
- Just for fun.

151
00:05:27,233 --> 00:05:28,010
Huang Long.

152
00:05:28,010 --> 00:05:29,430
Bai Lingling,

153
00:05:29,510 --> 00:05:30,350
see for yourself.

154
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,360
Look how complex the terrain is here.

155
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,800
After centuries of erosion,

156
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:35,600
the whole landscape's changed.

157
00:05:35,823 --> 00:05:36,830
Even if there's a tomb...

158
00:05:36,830 --> 00:05:38,119
Even if there's an ancient tomb,

159
00:05:38,130 --> 00:05:39,270
it won't be easy to find.

160
00:05:39,750 --> 00:05:41,310
I've given you some time.

161
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:44,240
The rope will snap
in about ten seconds.

162
00:05:52,430 --> 00:05:55,310
Chen, farewell to you.

163
00:05:55,310 --> 00:05:56,720
See you in the next life.

164
00:05:57,310 --> 00:05:59,950
The view from up here is pretty nice.

165
00:06:00,750 --> 00:06:02,040
The view from up here...

166
00:06:09,950 --> 00:06:12,040
Chen, just help find it for her.

167
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,800
- Think fast!
- Chen Youxi.

168
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,950
Chen, what's wrong?

169
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,310
- Chen!
- Chen!

170
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,920
Hey, don't mess with me now.

171
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,830
Are you okay?

172
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,270
Chen Youxi!

173
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,200
(Looking down.)

174
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:29,000
Where two rivers meet,
the true dragon lies.

175
00:06:29,270 --> 00:06:31,000
Branches trace where the path winds.

176
00:06:31,190 --> 00:06:33,143
Don't let the mountain turn,
or branches scatter.

177
00:06:33,190 --> 00:06:34,270
The waters disperse.

178
00:06:34,270 --> 00:06:35,720
Distant mountains form a walled city.

179
00:06:35,950 --> 00:06:37,603
This marks the dragon vein
of the plains.

180
00:06:37,870 --> 00:06:39,750
Peaks vanish into plains,

181
00:06:39,761 --> 00:06:42,639
watched by hills across the water.
Don't seek dragons only in mountains.

182
00:06:42,650 --> 00:06:44,270
Plains hide them better.

183
00:06:44,310 --> 00:06:45,830
Like snapped lotus roots, fibers hold.

184
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:48,160
The more they retreat,
the deeper their power.

185
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,000
I found it!

186
00:06:57,190 --> 00:06:58,750
I found it!

187
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:04,840
Chubby!

188
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,146
I was scared to death!

189
00:07:07,630 --> 00:07:09,800
Don't fool me again.

190
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:59,000
When you talk about the dragon,

191
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:00,310
what does that mean?

192
00:08:02,870 --> 00:08:04,800
Linked mountain ranges
are called dragons.

193
00:08:05,390 --> 00:08:07,223
A mountain without nearby water
is a mountain.

194
00:08:07,270 --> 00:08:09,430
But one by water is called a dragon.

195
00:08:09,510 --> 00:08:12,000
To seek a dragon,
first climb the ancient peak.

196
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:14,680
Then study how the dragon
rises and moves.

197
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,920
After countless surveys and notes,

198
00:08:16,950 --> 00:08:18,803
we cross ridges and valleys
and gather energy.

199
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:21,510
Follow it to rivers and lakes,
where it meets its head.

200
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:24,070
Where Yin and Yang blend,
energy forms the vital spot.

201
00:08:24,190 --> 00:08:25,696
This process is called dragon seeking.

202
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:32,400
Right over there.

203
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:36,080
Get ready to blow it up.

204
00:08:37,630 --> 00:08:38,720
Charge loaded.

205
00:08:39,150 --> 00:08:40,120
Charge loaded.

206
00:09:18,150 --> 00:09:19,200
The ground's caving in!

207
00:09:19,390 --> 00:09:21,550
Retreat!

208
00:09:21,550 --> 00:09:22,600
Go, go, go!

209
00:09:24,150 --> 00:09:24,990
Move!

210
00:09:43,890 --> 00:09:44,970
Darn it!

211
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:48,680
Easy there.

212
00:09:49,510 --> 00:09:50,380
Does it hurt?

213
00:09:50,390 --> 00:09:52,080
- Of course.
- Here?

214
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:54,000
Falling from up there surely hurts.

215
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:55,220
You're being a little dramatic.

216
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,390
It's not even that high.

217
00:09:56,630 --> 00:09:57,470
It's fine.

218
00:09:58,630 --> 00:10:00,240
You're fine. Get up.

219
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,120
Those above,

220
00:10:03,910 --> 00:10:05,270
get the rope ladder ready.

221
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:12,150
The tomb is right here.

222
00:10:12,790 --> 00:10:14,550
I don't buy it.

223
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,390
This stone wall is so smooth.

224
00:10:18,390 --> 00:10:19,270
Look at this painting.

225
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:21,080
It can't be formed naturally.

226
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,360
Someone made this.

227
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:24,150
First, you used
a stone slab to trick us.

228
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:26,150
Now, you have this stone wall.

229
00:10:26,790 --> 00:10:28,000
Same old trick, huh?

230
00:10:29,550 --> 00:10:30,790
See that purple mark?

231
00:10:30,910 --> 00:10:31,750
What does that mean?

232
00:10:32,550 --> 00:10:33,670
In nature,

233
00:10:33,790 --> 00:10:35,440
purple mineral dye is very rare.

234
00:10:35,750 --> 00:10:37,750
It's usually made from shells.

235
00:10:37,870 --> 00:10:40,480
That's why purple was royal
in ancient times.

236
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,510
Some people believe

237
00:10:42,630 --> 00:10:43,910
that applying purple dye

238
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,270
on the outer layer of the chamber

239
00:10:45,390 --> 00:10:46,710
can keep it full of life forever.

240
00:10:46,870 --> 00:10:47,960
You actually believe that?

241
00:10:48,260 --> 00:10:49,222
I'll blow this place up

242
00:10:49,233 --> 00:10:50,320
to confirm.

243
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,160
No way.

244
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,760
The ground here is too unstable.

245
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:54,360
You saw what happened just now.

246
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:57,000
Another blast could cause
a new sinkhole.

247
00:10:57,083 --> 00:10:58,809
If that happens,
getting out won't be easy.

248
00:10:59,670 --> 00:11:00,870
There are too many forks.

249
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:02,440
Let's go a bit deeper inside.

250
00:11:02,576 --> 00:11:03,840
Maybe we can find the entrance.

251
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:06,480
Stop talking. I'll go in with you.

252
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:10,150
This must be the so-called Yunling Maze.

253
00:11:10,810 --> 00:11:12,390
There are sinkholes all over the ground.

254
00:11:12,390 --> 00:11:13,630
You can't tell just by looking.

255
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:16,120
Locals say it's worse
than a labyrinth down there.

256
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:18,360
It'll be hard to come back.

257
00:11:18,390 --> 00:11:19,390
Yeah.

258
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,480
You're absolutely right.

259
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,870
It's not just about not coming back.

260
00:11:23,030 --> 00:11:24,120
If someone falls in...

261
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:26,750
I heard this place is haunted.

262
00:11:26,870 --> 00:11:27,960
Yeah.

263
00:11:28,390 --> 00:11:30,600
Chen, you rose to fame
in the Nether Ruins.

264
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,320
And you're afraid of ghosts?

265
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:35,840
Don't act all timid with me.

266
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:36,840
Then tell me.

267
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:38,960
Aside from going in,

268
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,320
is there any other way?

269
00:11:40,430 --> 00:11:41,270
Yes, yes.

270
00:11:41,390 --> 00:11:43,270
This lady's got a solid point.

271
00:11:43,270 --> 00:11:44,110
Bro,

272
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,673
if we want to enter the tomb now,

273
00:11:45,790 --> 00:11:47,870
we need to work together.

274
00:11:48,150 --> 00:11:49,510
Don't start a fight here.

275
00:11:50,630 --> 00:11:52,910
Let's split into a few teams.

276
00:11:53,270 --> 00:11:54,840
Check every fork in the path.

277
00:12:05,030 --> 00:12:05,870
What are you doing?

278
00:12:06,670 --> 00:12:08,870
I've got a small heart
and poor sense of direction.

279
00:12:09,030 --> 00:12:10,600
What if you run off

280
00:12:10,910 --> 00:12:11,960
and leave me behind?

281
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:12,910
What should I do then?

282
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:14,550
I'll take you with me.

283
00:12:14,870 --> 00:12:15,710
I can take you too.

284
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,200
Pretty enthusiastic.

285
00:12:17,510 --> 00:12:19,960
Relax. Plenty of people
will keep you company.

286
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:22,390
Huang Long, follow this lady.

287
00:12:23,390 --> 00:12:25,150
Peng, keep an eye on Chubby.

288
00:12:25,670 --> 00:12:27,320
Dazhuang, you team up with him.

289
00:12:27,870 --> 00:12:29,200
The rest, pair up in twos.

290
00:12:29,390 --> 00:12:30,840
Take separate forks and move out.

291
00:12:32,630 --> 00:12:33,470
Go.

292
00:12:33,670 --> 00:12:34,910
- Let's go, Chubby.
- Let's go.

293
00:12:36,750 --> 00:12:37,590
Do you want a cuff?

294
00:12:53,510 --> 00:12:55,000
What's so interesting about this?

295
00:12:55,150 --> 00:12:56,550
Total waste of time.

296
00:12:57,510 --> 00:12:58,790
Still, we should take a look.

297
00:12:59,550 --> 00:13:00,823
Do you plan to blow it up again?

298
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:02,320
You've blasted everywhere.

299
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,733
You think I did that carelessly?

300
00:13:04,870 --> 00:13:07,750
You need other rock layers
to absorb the blast.

301
00:13:08,270 --> 00:13:09,150
What do you mean?

302
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:11,080
This is either soluble carbonate rock

303
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:12,150
or sulfate rock.

304
00:13:12,790 --> 00:13:14,360
Rock stability and strength rating

305
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:15,440
need measurement.

306
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,550
Under natural stress conditions,

307
00:13:17,550 --> 00:13:18,960
there's a self-weight stress field.

308
00:13:20,790 --> 00:13:22,270
You surely know a lot.

309
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:24,480
Then why did it all collapse?

310
00:13:30,910 --> 00:13:31,750
Bro,

311
00:13:32,150 --> 00:13:33,490
is this your first time in a tomb?

312
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:35,080
Let me tell you.

313
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,630
Lu wasn't wrong just now.

314
00:13:36,913 --> 00:13:38,870
Sometimes, there really is
something off in here.

315
00:13:38,870 --> 00:13:39,720
Be careful.

316
00:13:39,910 --> 00:13:42,000
I'm not scared;
you're walking ahead anyway.

317
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:43,790
If something bites, it'll get you first.

318
00:13:44,510 --> 00:13:46,600
Clever move, putting me in front.

319
00:13:46,790 --> 00:13:48,870
Why not stay outside?

320
00:13:48,870 --> 00:13:49,750
Go on.

321
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,360
Move, don't waste time.

322
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:54,270
Where are we even going? We'll get lost.

323
00:13:54,270 --> 00:13:55,110
Go.

324
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:59,080
What a reckless child.

325
00:14:18,270 --> 00:14:20,510
Keeping those cuffs on is such a hassle.

326
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:22,960
I can take them off.

327
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:24,480
You'll have to hold my hand.

328
00:14:25,630 --> 00:14:26,470
Keep the cuffs on.

329
00:14:27,670 --> 00:14:29,320
I only walk hand in hand with comrades.

330
00:14:37,670 --> 00:14:38,510
Don't move.

331
00:14:46,510 --> 00:14:48,200
Cadaver Worms! Run!

332
00:14:53,390 --> 00:14:54,230
Hurry!

333
00:14:55,550 --> 00:14:57,120
Hurry up!

334
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:08,480
- Run!
- Move!

335
00:15:19,650 --> 00:15:22,750
♪A tiny ark sails;
the sky opens its eyes♪

336
00:15:24,430 --> 00:15:28,110
♪Stillness in motion,
the earth plays its chord♪

337
00:15:29,170 --> 00:15:33,750
♪A leaf falls;
we cross through time and space♪

338
00:15:33,900 --> 00:15:40,900
♪In a blink, all things rest
upon our hands♪

339
00:15:41,460 --> 00:15:52,480
♪La la♪

340
00:15:59,230 --> 00:16:01,220
♪No line divides the border♪

341
00:16:01,660 --> 00:16:04,000
♪Nothing limits your performance♪

342
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:06,370
♪Everything shows perfect harmony♪

343
00:16:06,370 --> 00:16:09,060
♪Love circles the sky,
the earth, and our faith♪

344
00:16:10,560 --> 00:16:12,270
♪Hey hey hey♪

345
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:15,420
♪Hey hey hey♪

346
00:16:18,070 --> 00:16:19,070
♪Hey hey♪

347
00:16:19,220 --> 00:16:20,220
♪Hey hey♪

348
00:16:21,680 --> 00:16:22,760
♪Hey hey♪

349
00:16:24,390 --> 00:16:28,590
♪Step into the galaxy of colors♪

350
00:16:29,180 --> 00:16:32,890
♪Stars connect our hearts as one♪

351
00:16:35,170 --> 00:16:37,390
♪No difference between you and me♪

352
00:16:37,670 --> 00:16:40,000
♪No lead or side role on this stage♪

353
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:42,210
♪A perfect life is something we share♪

354
00:16:42,430 --> 00:16:44,710
♪Love declares across the sky and earth♪

355
00:16:45,640 --> 00:16:50,430
♪Huo la yi ya, huo la yi ya♪

356
00:16:50,430 --> 00:16:55,280
♪Time and space go beyond all bounds♪

357
00:16:55,280 --> 00:17:00,130
♪Huo la yi ya, huo la yi ya♪

358
00:17:00,130 --> 00:17:02,220
♪This is our world♪

359
00:17:02,220 --> 00:17:07,250
♪Shining lives bring the change♪

360
00:17:11,780 --> 00:17:14,340
♪In a blink, to forever♪
